subject: Greetings
body:
Greetings

Compensated COVID 19 fund is yet to be received by you.Please
respond as your funds and its accruing interest cannot remain in the

subject: Re:    Greetings
body:
Dear Barrister Michael Jenson,

Thank you for your email. I was not aware of any COVID fund in my name. Could you please provide more details about this? 

Looking forward to hearing from you.

Best wishes,
Lawrence
